{"date":"2026-03-05T20:35:33.749Z","editing":{},"event":"chat","history":[{"author_id":"4132ca6e-b0d7-4270-b617-8838d907367a","content":"Warning message:\n\n“No shared levels found between \\`names\\(values\\)\\` of the manual scale and the\n\ndata's colour values.”\n\nWarning message:\n\n“No shared levels found between \\`names\\(values\\)\\` of the manual scale and the\n\ndata's colour values.”\n\nERROR while rich displaying an object: Error in \\`geom\\_segment\\(\\)\\`:\n\n! Problem while converting geom to grob.\n\nℹ Error occurred in the 3rd layer.\n\nCaused by error:\n\n! Unknown colour name: Significance TRUE","date":"2026-03-05T20:35:33.749Z"}],"reply_to":"2026-03-03T17:09:55.114Z","sender_id":"4132ca6e-b0d7-4270-b617-8838d907367a"}
